latestIgtvVideos.title: SS’21 Fresh colour blocking
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Pairing colours from different families could be chaotic, but let’s just say 2021 screams harmony(atleast I’d like to believe so) 😝 2021 is a power surge of colours and I couldn’t help but create a few looks that are super saturated yet in harmony, refreshing yet not brash🤩 
Look 1: 
A modern take of keeping it simple by adding one solid colour to maximise your look. 

Look 2: 
The goal here is to be playful and make a statement with colours! Maybe for days when I don’t feel good at all, colours could be a good pick me up 😉

Look 3:
Rich colours paired together could be a bold choice but it also says “YES I HAVE ARRIVED” 

Look 4:
A fitting combination and meant for everyone to try! Don’t miss out on the denims cinched at the bottom 😉 It could take your outfit from 0 to 100 💯 

Look 5:
2021 monochrome will see single contrast shades into monotones to create depth and visual intrigue 

Look 6:
This look screams “CONFIDENCE”. Knowing what colors go together is a skill in itself and it can have a positive impact on all areas of your life.
Let me know your favourite look🥰

#IGTV #Pantone2021 #ColourBlocking #outfits #Timbaland #videocreator #indiancreator

A little about the styles :
🌸Saree : @myntra (9038857)🌸

latestPosts.caption:
We won! 🤍 🥇 
I couldn’t say much on stage because I didn’t know what to say but more on that later!! ITS A WIN FOR ME AND FOR YOU GUYS cause I know how much my lovely beautiful community motivates me🤍 I know awards are nice but I’ll tell you what’s nicer is that on days you feel down and demotivated, someone texts you saying ki they feel angry that I am not at 1M, someone texts me saying how I have made a difference in their life, someone tells me how I’m a friend to them and more! 
It’s always the love that you’ll receive and you take forward in your life ♥️ Big thanks to my team @riag07 for hyping me like the best girl in the world, hearing me rant all day long and the never ending support! Thank you @myntra for making this and so many incredible things that have happened in all these years of my journey with you! Thank you to my friends who are always helping me in so many ways I can’t even talk about! Thank you to my boyfriend who is truly my best cheerleader and my guiding star 🌟 
Thank you to “TANUMITA” because she makes it happen all day everyday ♥️ 

OmNamahShivaya 🙏🏼
